36
00:01:53,300 --> 00:01:54,700
<i>Sebaiknya kau tidak menemuinya.</i>

37
00:01:55,367 --> 00:01:56,601
<i>Maksudku, Nona Jahyeon.</i>

38
00:01:57,934 --> 00:01:59,635
<i>Anda Siap?</i>

39
00:01:59,767 --> 00:02:00,934
<i>Dimana Kepala
