<i>Dimana Nona Jahyeon?</i>

41
00:02:02,501 --> 00:02:04,168
<i>Kenapa Anda membuat
keributan seperti ini!?</i>

42
00:02:04,267 --> 00:02:05,667
<i>Pangeran ada di sini.</i>

43
00:02:07,501 --> 00:02:08,735
<i>Dia masih hidup.</i>

44
00:02:10,234 --> 00:02:11,701
<i>Dia datang kesini
untuk bertemu denganmu.</i>

45
00:02:15,834 --> 00:02:16,668
<i>Nona Ja Hyeon!</i>

46
00:02:17,300 --> 00:02:18,700
<i>- Nona Ja Hyeon!
- Yang Mulia!</i>

47
00:02:20,033 --> 00:02:21,667
<i>Nona Jahyeon!</i>

48
